                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8992" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0410</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1196 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从强硬到理解：昌盛公司的员工离职补偿冲突</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Rigidity to Understanding: The Labor Dispute over Severance Compensation at Changsheng Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨桂菊，周怡辰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">常熟市昌盛经编织造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">离职补偿；离职冲突；罗宾斯冲突理论；员工关系管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Severance Compensation; Severance Conflict; Robbins&#39; Conflict Theory; Employee Relations Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在现代企业管理中，员工关系处理的重要性不断上升，员工冲突正是其中严峻的挑战，如若处理不当，将触发的一连串组织危机。本案例客观地描述了昌盛公司在面临员工小李的离职补偿争议时所经历的内部矛盾和冲突。随着小李的不满情绪和对抗行为的逐步升级，公司内部出现了利益、目标和认知上的分歧，这些分歧最终演变成了影响公司稳定和运营的严重冲突。冲突的持续升级不仅影响了日常生产，还导致公司管理层面临巨大压力，最终促使副总经理林介入，采取了一系列措施来缓和矛盾、恢复生产，并逐步重建了公司的和谐与秩序。本案例希望通过昌盛公司的离职冲突危机，启发学生思考离职冲突产生原因和对组织的影响，以及如何有效解决冲突危机实现和谐的组织关系。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In modern enterprise management, the importance of employee relationship is rising, and employee conflict is a serious challenge. If handled improperly, it will trigger a series of organizational crises. This case objectively describes the internal contradictions and conflicts that Changsheng Company experienced when facing the employee Xiao Li&#39;s resignation compensation dispute. With the gradual escalation of Xiao Li&#39;s discontent and confrontational behavior, differences in interests, goals and cognition emerged within the company, which eventually evolved into serious conflicts affecting the company&#39;s stability and operation. The continuous escalation of the conflict not only affected the daily production, but also caused the company&#39;s management to face great pressure, and finally prompted the deputy general manager Lin to intervene, take a series of measures to ease the contradiction, resume production, and gradually rebuild the company&#39;s harmony and order. This case hopes to inspire students to think about the causes of turnover conflict and its impact on the organization through the turnover conflict crisis of Changsheng Company, and how to effectively solve the conflict crisis to achieve a harmonious organizational relationship.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">离职原因；冲突定义；引发冲突的条件；冲突类型；冲突影响；冲突过程；冲突管理策略；冲突预防</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
